Pre-Game Insights: Haiti will face Sint Maarten on September 9, 2024, as part of the CONCACAF Nations League.
The match is scheduled to take place at 5:00 p.m. at the Estadio Centroamericano in Mayagüez, Puerto Rico.
Haiti's team, the Grenadiers, are coming off a 4-1 victory against Puerto Rico.
French coach Sébastien Migné discussed the team's state of mind and preparation for the match against Sint Maarten, emphasizing an ambitious project that extends to the World Cup qualifiers.
